I loved this food even though it took forever to make.
I don't have any time to translate this because i'm busy doing to 50 math problems if someone could i help i would greatly appreciate it.
Thank you So much.

item.title: Spainsh Help
item.dc:creator: @Mod_Adam Adam
item.description:
@Mod_Adam wrote:

Translators suck, they translate word for word. Some languages, such as Spanish, don’t. In Spanish, you say, “The bus school.” Not, “The school bus.”

Correct Spanish:
el bus escolar

Translators way (Might actually do it correct on this example, but not all):
el escolar bus
